# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Avalanche RPC endpoints (OPTIONAL)
#
# Both variables below are PUBLIC, browser-exposed values. Vite inlines any
# VITE_-prefixed variable into the client bundle, so whatever URL you set here
# is visible to anyone who loads the site. Only use endpoints that are safe to
# expose (e.g. origin/domain-allowlisted). NEVER put a secret/keyed RPC URL here
# unless the provider restricts that key by origin/domain.
#
# Leave BOTH blank to use the built-in public defaults (current behaviour):
#   primary  = https://api.avax.network/ext/bc/C/rpc
#   fallback = https://rpc.ankr.com/avalanche
#
# Set VITE_AVALANCHE_RPC_PRIMARY to route through a dedicated provider (e.g.
# Chainstack) as the primary. The public fallback below stays active.
# VITE_AVALANCHE_RPC_FALLBACK optionally replaces the secondary (Ankr) endpoint.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_AVALANCHE_RPC_PRIMARY=
VITE_AVALANCHE_RPC_FALLBACK=
